{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, he was terrified and convinced that as soon as they found out that he was Jewish that they would, you know, kill him in his sleep or something less desirable.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so children were allowed to visit their fathers once or twice a week at the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we made a big show, my father and I, because both of us were fluent in French, of talking French, appearing French, acting French, and getting the idea across that that was really our nationality.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And here we were in the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Our daily fare was one big bowl of what they call lentil soup.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There weren't many lentils in it, nor anything else.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was generally a dishwater kind of situation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were grateful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some of the bread was moldy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The thing that I remember perhaps in a most embarrassing and distasteful way was that the hygienic facilities were trenchers with two-by-fours over them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And whenever you, you needed to go there, which you tried to avoid at all cost, a soldier with a mounted bayonet came with you to make sure that there was no escape.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I will never understand why this system was such, but it was a very difficult thing to deal with, especially for youngsters heading into puberty and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "As the German army approached then, the French, our French soldiers who guarding us, were giving instructions that they were to walk us inland, away from the approaching German troops.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in the camp, conditions were really sort of so-so.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There were women that delivered babies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were women that had delivered babies while we were on, on our march, or walk, or whatever you want to call it.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
